Class Profile

java.lang.Object
clinic.Profile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Profile>
public class Profile extends Object implements Comparable<Profile>
Represents a profile for a patient, including personal details such as name and date of birth. This class implements the Comparable interface to enable comparison between Profile objects.
Author:
Dhawal Arora (Netid: da812)
